Seeker Android app

All apps in this repo are downloaded from github releases automatically.

Currently it serves 1 apps. To add it to your F-Droid client, scan the QR code (click it to enlarge) or use this URL:

https://raw.githubusercontent.com/efreak/seeker-fdroid/main/fdroid/repo
